graph TD
    t_load[Load one Q tile<br/>into SRAM]
    t_load --> t_loop[Loop over KV tiles]
    t_loop --> t_kv[Load K,V tile<br/>into SRAM]
    t_kv --> t_compute[Block score update<br/>with online softmax]
    t_compute --> t_accum[Accumulate output<br/>and write final tile]
    t_compute --> t_loop
